1. Product Overview & Mission
What Chirp.bet Is [VISION]
A real-time MLB over/under edge detection platform. It scans every live MLB game, combines pitcher fatigue, batter power, wind, park factors, runner situations, and temperature into a multiplier-stack model, and surfaces actionable over/under edges ranked by conviction level.
The One-Line Pitch
See the edge before the line moves.
What It Is NOT
Not a sportsbook. Not a picks service. Not a social platform. It is a data tool that surfaces statistical edges for entertainment purposes.

What Currently Exists [CURRENT]
"Chirpbot" — a 6-sport (MLB, NFL, NCAAF, NBA, WNBA, CFL) real-time alert
platform with 94 alert cylinder modules, AI enrichment via GPT-4o, gambling
insights composition, and Telegram/web delivery. The MLB probability engine
already implements the 6-factor multiplier-stack model from this spec. The
Chirp.bet rebuild would narrow the focus to MLB-only over/under edge detection
with a dedicated frontend.

Target User
MLB bettors aged 25-45 who already bet over/unders and want a data edge. They use FanDuel/DraftKings, follow baseball, and are comfortable with stats like ERA, ISO, and park factors. They check their phone during games.

Chirp Levels [CURRENT — already implemented in mlb-prob-model.ts]
Level         Edge %    Color           Meaning
STRONG CHIRP  12%+      #EF4444 (Red)   Highest conviction — multiple factors stacking hard
CHIRP         7-12%     #F59E0B (Amber) Solid edge — worth acting on
SOFT CHIRP    4-7%      #3B82F6 (Blue)  Worth watching — conditions developing

Classification uses blended score: 50% edge composite + 30% p_event + 20% leverage.


